Interface MessageMap

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Cloneable
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface MessageMap
extends Cloneable
    Sequence of handler targets that should be passed by message. TODO: should it be added as a required field for message? TODO: create a builder for all kind of maps. Make concrete implementations package-local.
